headline: Lennox Invests in AI Agents to Enhance Technician Support and Customer Experience
summary: Lennox (NYSE: LII), a leading provider of innovative climate control solutions, is accelerating its digital transformation through strategic investments in AI-powered tools designed to enhance the customer experience.
